title: Murphy and the Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series
text:
> Sports Murphy and the Mets sweep Cubs to reach World Series The New York Mets celebrate after Game 4 of the National League baseball championship series against the Chicago Cubs Wednesday, Oct. 21, 2015, in Chicago. The Mets won 8-3 to advance to the World Series. (AP Photo/Nam Y. Huh) The most compelling, sharable stories from across the web.
